      <ID>1</ID>
      <DefaultText>[Player Name],

Short of [url=glossary:kyros]Kyros[/url]' direct interdiction, I remain the sovereign adjudicator of disputes between any two living creatures protected by [url=glossary:kyros]Kyros[/url]' Peace. I have ordered [url=glossary:graven ashe]Graven Ashe[/url] and [url=glossary:the voices of nerat]the Voices of Nerat[/url] to cease all violence - both have disobeyed.

That the two Archons are insubordinate is beyond any doubt. Deciding whether either of them is actively treacherous requires a most thorough examination, for the punishment of death cannot be reversed.

As my agent, arbiter, and deputy, you are above the petty customs of the [url=glossary:disfavored]Disfavored[/url] and [url=glossary:scarlet chorus]Scarlet Chorus[/url]. You are not, however, above my law. You still answer to me - and you WILL answer to me at once. Report immediately to the [url=glossary:bastard city]Bastard City[/url] to explain your actions at [url=glossary:vendrien's well]Vendrien's Well[/url]...

-[url=glossary:tunon]Tunon[/url] the Adjudicator, Archon of Justice</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <ID>3</ID>
      <DefaultText>Ask for additional resources.</DefaultText>
      <FemaleText />
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
